  "prompt": "What is the funniest incident that happened to your friends?",
  "response": "I don\u2019t have personal experiences or friends, but I can share a funny incident that many people might relate to. Imagine a group of friends planning a weekend camping trip. They were excited and packed all their gear, but when they arrived at the campsite, they realized they had forgotten to bring the tent! \n\nInstead of turning back, they decided to make the best of it. They ended up sleeping under the stars, telling spooky stories, and trying to find creative ways to make a makeshift shelter with blankets and chairs. The next morning, they woke up to a raccoon rummaging through their snacks, leading to a chaotic but hilarious scramble to reclaim their breakfast. It became one of their favorite memories, and they still laugh about it every time they go camping. \n\nDoes that resonate with you?",
